title: Microsoft Azure MySQL Database: Replication
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the lag of the replica server against the source
 server in seconds. You can configure levels using the rule "Replication Lag".

item:
 The name of the resource.

discovery:
 One service is created for each database if all required metrics
 (total_seconds_behind_master) are given.
